                  <h2>This week's practice comment:</h2>
                  <ul>
                    <li>
                      <a href="/break-time/practice-comment/shared-governance-has-given-us-the-power-of-collaboration/7001483.article">
                        <img src="http://www.nursingtimes.net/pictures/360xAny/4/6/3/3003463_team-meeting.jpg" alt="Team meeting multidisciplinary working" />
                      </a>
                      <h3>
                        <a href="/break-time/practice-comment/shared-governance-has-given-us-the-power-of-collaboration/7001483.article">'Shared governance has given us the power of collaboration'</a>
                      </h3>
                      <p class="standfirst">The trust where I work has established a system of shared governance. Staff have collective ownership to develop and improve practice, to ensure patients receive caring, safe and confident care.</p>
